                    <div class="col-md-6 body-text">
                        <h1>Specialising in tax consultancy for over 30 years.</h1>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row gx-5">
                    <div class="col-md-6 body-text">
                        <p>I've been a tax adviser for 35 years, working in regional, national and international accountancy firms. In that time, I've worked with businesses of all sizes and helped all sorts of people with their personal tax affairs. I’ve been independent since 2013, using that wealth of experience to provide a direct, one-to-one service.</p>
                        <p>You already know that tax can be complicated. My aim is to make it simpler, so you can plan your business or personal finances with greater certainty.</p>
                        <p>I could show a list of services but that would be boring and probably unhelpful. It's likely that I'll have helped someone with similar tax problems or opportunities as you, so why not talk it over and see what can be done? The tax savings could be substantial - as could the cost of doing nothing or getting it wrong.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 body-text">
                        <p>If you're an accountant, solicitor or other professional adviser and would like to discuss tax with an experienced specialist, on a non-competitive basis, please get in touch. I provide confidential, specialist tax help to several firms, helping them enhance the service they give to their clients.</p>
                        <p>There’s no charge for an initial consultation and my fees are highly competitive for someone with my experience.</p>
                    <p>Let's talk.</p>
                    </div>
